comments: Oubre Jr. (PHI) is established in Jones Jr.'s (DAL) path when he absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
Washington (DAL) slightly extends his arm into Harris' (PHI) body during the drive, which he is able to move through.
Maxey (PHI) receives the pass, gathers on his left foot, and maintains his pivot foot at the start of his dribble.
Maxey (PHI) steps out of bounds while still in possession of the ball.
Irving (DAL) legally contests Lowry's (PHI) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Jones Jr. (DAL) brushes Oubre Jr.'s (PHI) arm during the drive as the contact that occurs during the drive is marginal.
Doncic (DAL) makes contact with Oubre Jr.'s (PHI) arm after he releases the ball on his pass attempt, which is marginal.
Green (DAL) establishes himself in Harris' (PHI) path and absorbs the incoming contact during the screen.
Doncic (DAL) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two steps before his jump shot attempt.
Batum (PHI) has a resting hand on Washington's (DAL) body while defending the shot attempt, the contact is compounded after Batum is pushed in the back.
Maxey (PHI) takes more than 8 seconds to establish himself in the frontcourt.
Oubre Jr. (PHI) establishes himself in Green's (DAL) path and absorbs the incoming contact during the pick.
Washington (DAL) reaches in and grazes Harris' (PHI) body during the drive as he is able to move through the contact.
Washington (DAL) is established in Harris' (PHI) path when he engages and disengages with him during the screen.
Irving (DAL) reaches in and contact with Lowry's (PHI) arm that affects his control of the ball in the backcourt.
Lowry (PHI) calls for and is granted a timeout before eight seconds.
Green (DAL) commits a take foul on Maxey (PHI).
Batum (PHI) legally contests Doncic's (DAL) jump shot attempt.
Kleber (DAL) commits a take foul on Batum (PHI).
Kleber (DAL) commits a take foul on Oubre Jr. (PHI).
Oubre Jr. (PHI) reaches in and makes clean contact to the ball as he defends Washington (DAL).
